bc4baf59141f3b6bfe601bc943911f33","tid":176770,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213ad51220c7df347ce39f68fbda438c989d9bba","tid":176770,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"咪返黎"},{"pid":"6a524acd7c038976f4856b1b1dc1fcca9108a6b3","tid":176770,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:25:11.000Z","msg":"我想屌佢個咀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e6a6d52cb2c2d75ca31e73c61bc6431702a560","tid":176770,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170328/large/1490632292_08d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F1490632292_08d8.jpg&h=8c2b012f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170328/large/1490632291_8b14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F1490632291_8b14.jpg&h=4a7e8b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚10時許，一名身穿及膝白裙的女子行經黃大仙下邨巴士總站時，發現遭一名形迹可疑的男子尾隨，其間感到遭人用手機偷拍裙底，更開有閃燈拍攝。偷拍男被揭發後一度欲走過馬路逃跑，幸有多名熱心途人相助，將偷拍男截獲，其中4名猛男更將男人壓在地上，動彈不得。<br />\n<br />\n讀者王小姐表示，當時剛落車不久，看到4個男仔追偷拍男，然後將他撳低在地下制服，其間偷拍男想將手機內照片刪除，但被人制止，王小姐拍下4男勇擒偷拍狂片段，及聽到女事主稱「如果唔係你開閃光燈，我都唔知你影我呀!」，而片中受害女事主一度激動，向偷拍狂大嗌：「冇話對唔住大晒呀！」有女途人從旁安慰，她不禁氣憤的說：「嬲架！佢無啦啦偷影我呀！」<br />\n<br />\n事後警員到場，將偷拍狂拘捕，更邀請有份幫忙的熱心途人提供資料，受害女事主更即場向出手相助的途人鞠躬道謝：「唔該晒呀！真係唔該晒你哋呀！」<br />\n警方表示昨晚約10時，一名27歲女事主行經黃大仙正德街一條扶手電梯時，被尾隨同齡姓劉男子用手機偷拍裙底，女事主大驚，並通知35歲丈夫報警，事件驚動其他途人，男子最終涉嫌遊蕩被捕。<br />\n<br />\n沙勞ching係咪奶左野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7252957d6a92aa551a7341189ec40da5c9584745","tid":176770,"uid":79735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b26f5c3057cacd5c309071302a13c51d6e9af7","tid":176770,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"玩留"},{"pid":"cc87ba048ef90fe2955ca0f449aacd442d47da6e","tid":176770,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee0397b300563a998b4b03b1a2aee3c2e03280a","tid":176770,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"沙洛文.監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e5a6db5137700be021cc11494b0e882ad9915c","tid":176770,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙洛文.監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d06034b53b2c9a44430e8d1c4b1417cea46fe1d","tid":176770,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"監獄文-卡勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h